msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.121:0.2"
msgid "12. Lokakāmaguṇavagga"
msgstr "12. The World and the Kinds of Sensual Stimulation"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 121. Rāhulovādasutta → rāhuḷovādasuttaṃ (bj) | rāhula (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.121:0.3"
msgid "121. Rāhulovādasutta"
msgstr "121. Advice to Rāhula"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavato rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko "
"udapādi:"
msgstr "Then as he was in private retreat this thought came to his mind:"

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.3"
msgid "“paripakkā kho rāhulassa vimuttiparipācaniyā dhammā;"
msgstr "“The qualities that ripen in freedom have ripened in Rāhula."

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.4"
msgid "yannūnāhaṃ rāhulaṃ uttariṃ āsavānaṃ khaye vineyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I lead him further to the ending of defilements?”"

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiyaṃ "
"piṇḍāya caritvā "
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, "
"wandered for alms in Sāvatthī. "

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.6"
msgid "pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"After the meal, on his return from alms-round, he addressed Venerable Rāhula:"

#. VAR: rāhula → rāhuḷa (bj)
msgctxt "sn35.121:1.7"
msgid "“gaṇhāhi, rāhula, nisīdanaṃ."
msgstr "“Rāhula, get your sitting cloth."

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.8"
msgid "Yena andhavanaṃ tenupasaṅkamissāma divāvihārāyā”ti."
msgstr "Let’s go to the Dark Forest for the day’s meditation.”"

msgctxt "sn35.121:1.9"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā rāhulo bhagavato paṭissutvā nisīdanaṃ ādāya "
"bhagavantaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandhi."
msgstr ""
"“Yes, sir,” replied Rāhula. Taking his sitting cloth he followed behind the "
"Buddha."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.106"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena anekāni devatāsahassāni bhagavantaṃ anubandhāni honti:"
msgstr ""
"Now at that time many thousands of deities followed the Buddha, thinking:"

msgctxt "sn35.121:2.2"
msgid "“ajja bhagavā āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ uttariṃ āsavānaṃ khaye vinessatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Today the Buddha will lead Rāhula further to the ending of defilements!”"

msgctxt "sn35.121:2.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle paññatte "
"āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha plunged deep into the Dark Forest and sat at the root of a "
"tree on the seat spread out."

msgctxt "sn35.121:2.4"
msgid "Āyasmāpi kho rāhulo bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "Rāhula bowed to the Buddha and sat down to one side."

msgctxt "sn35.121:2.5"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:3.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rāhula, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Rāhula? "

msgctxt "sn35.121:3.2"
msgid "cakkhu niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "Is the eye permanent or impermanent?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:4.1"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:5.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:6.1"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.”"

