msgctxt "sn35.121:45.1"
msgid ""
"“Yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ, saññāgataṃ, "
"saṅkhāragataṃ, viññāṇagataṃ, tampi niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
