#. <a class="sc" id="sc50"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:50.1"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc51"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:51.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmimpi nibbindati, rūpesupi "
"nibbindati, cakkhuviññāṇepi nibbindati, cakkhusamphassepi nibbindati, "
"yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ "
"saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, "
"sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact. And they become disillusioned "
"with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness "
"that arises conditioned by eye contact. "

msgctxt "sn35.121:51.2"
msgid ""
"jivhāyapi nibbindati, rasesupi nibbindati, jivhāviññāṇepi nibbindati, "
"jivhāsamphassepi nibbindati, yampidaṃ jivhāsamphassapaccayā uppajjati "
"vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati … pe …."
msgstr "They grow disillusioned with the ear … nose … tongue … body …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc52"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:52.1"
msgid ""
"Manasmimpi nibbindati, dhammesupi nibbindati, manoviññāṇepi nibbindati, "
"manosamphassepi nibbindati, yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati "
"vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, and mind contact. And they grow "
"disillusioned with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and "
"consciousness that arises conditioned by mind contact."

msgctxt "sn35.121:52.2"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn35.121:52.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc53"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.121:53.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn35.121:53.2"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā rāhulo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandi."
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Rāhula was happy with what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn35.121:53.3"
msgid ""
"Imasmiñca pana veyyākaraṇasmiṃ bhaññamāne āyasmato rāhulassa anupādāya "
"āsavehi cittaṃ vimucci."
msgstr ""
"And while this discourse was being spoken, Rāhula’s mind was freed from "
"defilements by not grasping."

msgctxt "sn35.121:53.4"
msgid "Anekānañca devatāsahassānaṃ virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"And the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in those thousands "
"of deities:"

msgctxt "sn35.121:53.5"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti."
msgstr "“Everything that has a beginning has an end.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.121:53.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
